sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>SubscriptionScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>CancelSubscription / Resubscribe
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Subscription
  A->>B: open Subscription
  B-->>A: status, renews-at, $9.99/mo (simulated)
  A->>B: tap Cancel
  B->>C: cancel()
  C->>E: updateSubscription(status = cancelled)
  note right of E: payment simulated —<br/>access until period end
  E-->>C: Subscription (cancelled)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (cancelled)
  B-->>A: status updated
  note over E: planned — updateSubscription<br/>via SupabaseGateway (RLS)
